---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Cadets1 from 'src/assets/images/Cadets1.jpg';
import Cadets2 from 'src/assets/images/Cadets2.jpg';
import Cadets3 from 'src/assets/images/Cadets3.jpg';
import Cadets4 from 'src/assets/images/Cadets4.jpg';
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <section class="border-b border-white/20 bg-accent-500 py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl border-x border-white/20 px-8 py-12 gradient-grid">
      <div class="mx-auto text-white text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-display uppercase">Army cadets</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-black text-white py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8">
      <a href="/" class="bg-orange text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300">
        Return to Main Page
      </a>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8">Army Cadets</h2>
      <p>
        <br>
        Joining the Army Cadet Force was a transformative experience that enriched my life in several ways. 
        Cadets provided me with opportunities that extended far beyond conventional learning, allowing me to develop skills and create memories that will last a lifetime.
        <br>
        <br>
        Throughout my time at cadets, I had the privilege of participating in a variety of activities that identified my abilities and broadened my horizons. 
        Attending several week-long summer camps and weekend excursions, I engaged in adventure training that pushed me beyond my comfort zone. 
        Rough camping in all weather conditions taught me resilience, while working with the L98A2 rifle was both educational and a new responsibility that I was entrusted with. 
        Not only did I fire the rifle live on shooting ranges, but I also learned how to disassemble, clean, and maintain it. 
        This experience deepened my understanding of the importance of upkeep and safety, instilling in me a strong sense of responsibility to maintain equipment properly.
        <br>
        <br>
